{"article_id":"AmxdiIxwwAPnalIY","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"A defiant acting Attorney General Matthew Whitaker declared to Congress on Friday","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"that he had not interfered with special counsel Robert Mueller 's investigation","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"and that his handling of the case had been `` independent of any outside interference . ''","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"\" I have not interfered in any way with the special counsel ' s investigation , ''","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Whitaker told the House Judiciary Committee during a combative hearing","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"in which lawmakers repeatedly pressed him for details on his handling of the criminal investigations","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"surrounding President Donald Trump .","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"In more than four hours of sworn testimony on Friday , Whitaker sought to answer criticisms","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that have shadowed his time","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"leading a Justice Department","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"conducting tandem criminal investigations","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"surrounding the president .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Whitaker is a close ally of Trump","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"and Democrats have suggested","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"he might have been chosen for the job","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"because he had publicly criticized Mueller 's probe","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"before being put in a position","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"to lead it .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"Want news from on WhatsApp ?","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Click this link on your mobile device","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"to get started","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Whitaker said","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"he had `` not talked to the president of the United States about the special counsel . ''","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"He said","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"he had not discussed it with any other senior White House officials ,","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"that he had not denied investigators resources","depth":15},{"id":27,"text":"to do their work","depth":15},{"id":28,"text":"and suggested to the committee 's chairman , Rep. Jerrold Nadler , D-N.Y. ,","depth":15},{"id":29,"text":"that he had not stepped in","depth":16},{"id":30,"text":"to thwart any of the steps","depth":17},{"id":31,"text":"Mueller planned to take in his investigation .","depth":17},{"id":32,"text":"So far ,","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"Whitaker said ,","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"`` there has been no event","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"- no decision -","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"that has required me to take any action '' in the case .","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"Still , in his first and likely only appearance before Congress as the attorney general , Whitaker told lawmakers","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"that he would not give them any more detail about his conversations with Trump ,","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"sparring with House Democrats","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"eager to know","depth":15},{"id":41,"text":"whether the White House had sought to interfere in the investigations","depth":16},{"id":42,"text":"centered on the president .","depth":16},{"id":43,"text":"He also repeatedly declined to give them more specific information about Mueller 's investigation","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"because it is ongoing .","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"\" Your failure","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"to respond fully to our questions here today","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"in no way limits the ability of this committee","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"to get answers in the long run ,","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"even if you are a private citizen","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"when we finally learn the truth , \"","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"Nadler said .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"Nadler closed the hearing","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"by saying","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"the committee would call back Whitaker , under subpoena","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"if necessary ,","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"for a closed-door interview","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"to get `` more fulsome '' answers to questions .","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"That promise capped hours of feisty","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"- and for many Democrats seemingly unsatisfying -","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"exchanges","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"centered mostly on the investigation","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"Trump has dismissed as a hoax and a witch hunt .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"For most of the day , Whitaker refused to say much at all about the probe or his own views of it ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"including whether he agreed with Trump 's characterization .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"\" Are you overseeing a witch hunt ? \"","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"asked Rep. Steve Cohen , D-Tenn .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Whitaker said","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"it would be `` inappropriate for me to comment on an ongoing investigation . ''","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"Background :","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"Who is Matthew Whitaker ?","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Hawkeye football star and federal prosecutor becomes acting attorney general","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"The much-anticipated confrontation lived up its billing as the first major clash between the White House and Democrats","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"who took control of the House of Representatives in January .","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"The hearing came","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"days after Trump used his State of the Union speech Tuesday","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"to criticize `` ridiculous partisan investigations . ''","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"But House Speaker Nancy Pelosi , D-Calif. , called the statement a threat","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"lawmakers would be delinquent","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"if they did n't conduct oversight investigations .","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"At one point","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"when Nadler pressed for answers ,","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"Whitaker cut off the chairman ,","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"saying :","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"\" Mr . Chairman , I see","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"that your five minutes are up . \"","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"The comment prompted a roar of laughter through the hearing room gallery ,","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"taking even Nadler by surprise .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Before an early break in the hearing , a combative Whitaker urged members to address \" the real work \" of the Justice Department ,","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"referring to the lawmakers ' intense focus on the special counsel ' s investigation .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"\" We haven ' t talked about the work","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"related to violent crime , \"","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"Whitaker told the panel .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"\" I look forward to talking about the substance of the work at the Department of Justice . \"","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"One of the testiest exchanges came","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"when Rep. Sheila Jackson Lee , D-Texas , asked","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"about whether Whitaker had passed along information about the Mueller investigation to Trump , his former chief of staff John Kelly or others .","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"Whitaker declined to talk about what he told administration officials ,","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"but the lawmaker bristled in an exchange about the time","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"left for her questions .","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"\" We ' re not joking here , \"","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"Jackson Lee said .","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"\" Your humor is not acceptable . \"","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"The committee 's senior Republican , Rep. Doug Collins of Georgia , however , warned the witness at the start of the hearing","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"to prepare for \" a long day .","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"\" \" If you have been watching TV recently ,","depth":15},{"id":107,"text":"you know","depth":16},{"id":108,"text":"what this is going to be about , \"","depth":16},{"id":109,"text":"Collins said .","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"`` This is nothing more than an exercise in character assassination . ''","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"But Rep. Hakeem Jeffries , D-N.Y. , was unfazed ,","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"saying","depth":15},{"id":113,"text":"that it was important to examine Whitaker ' s background .","depth":15},{"id":114,"text":"\" Who are you","depth":17},{"id":115,"text":"and how in the heck did you become of the head of the Department of Justice ? \"","depth":17},{"id":116,"text":"Jeffries said at one point ,","depth":16},{"id":117,"text":"cutting Whitaker off","depth":16},{"id":118,"text":"before he could respond .","depth":16},{"id":119,"text":"\" In the final week , keep your hands off the Mueller investigation . \"","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"Clearly unsatisfied with Whitaker ' s refusal","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"to more fully discuss his communications with the president and his oversight of the Mueller investigation ,","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"Nadler said","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"he was planning to re-call Whitaker at another date for a deposition","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"where he would be questioned further .","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"The Senate could move as early as this week to confirm his permanent replacement , William Barr .","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"Whitaker clashed repeatedly with lawmakers","depth":6},{"id":127,"text":"pushing for details","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"on how he had been selected to lead the Justice Department , his decision","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"not to recuse himself from overseeing Mueller 's work and the trajectory of that investigation .","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"Whitaker has been a polarizing figure since the start of his time as attorney general .","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"Some Democrats and Republicans had questioned","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"whether his appointment was legal","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"because he had not been confirmed by the Senate .","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"Then Whitaker said","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"he disregarded advice from the department ' s career ethics lawyers","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"that he disqualify himself from overseeing the Russia investigation","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"because of comments","depth":15},{"id":138,"text":"he ' d made","depth":16},{"id":139,"text":"before joining the department","depth":16},{"id":140,"text":"that questioned the inquiry","depth":15},{"id":141,"text":"and suggested","depth":16},{"id":142,"text":"it could be starved of funding .","depth":16},{"id":143,"text":"`` I made that decision","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"and I stand by that decision , ''","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"Whitaker told Rep. Hank Johnson , D-Ga.","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"Ethics officials told him","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"that it was a `` close call ''","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"and that `` my other public statements recognized the professionalism and competence of the special counsel , ''","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"Lawmakers of both parties asked","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"whether Whitaker had changed his opinion of the Mueller investigation ,","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"but he refused to answer them","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"because he said","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"it remains incomplete .","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"\" I am not going to characterize that investigation","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"or give you my opinion about that investigation","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"as I sit here today , ''","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"Whitaker told Rep. Andy Biggs , R-Ariz .","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"Whitaker said last month","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"that the investigation was \" close to being completed , \" the first time","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"anyone familiar with its inner workings had offered even a hint in public of its likely trajectory .","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"He did not elaborate at the time","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"and he declined to tell lawmakers what he meant .","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"`` Bob Mueller is going to finish his investigation","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"when he wants to finish his investigation , ''","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"Whitaker said .","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"Whitaker sought to dismiss suggestions","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"that he was initially hired at the Justice Department","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"because of his past criticism of the Mueller investigation .","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"the decision","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"to hire him as then-Attorney General Sessions ' chief of staff ,","depth":13},{"id":173,"text":"was \" Sessions ' decision","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"to make .","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"And he offered me the job . \"","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"Whitaker said","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"he \" didn ' t have a relationship with anyone at the White House . ''","depth":11},{"id":178,"text":"But he did acknowledge","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"first interviewing for a job as special White House counsel in charge","depth":13},{"id":180,"text":"of coordinating the administration 's dealings with Mueller 's team .","depth":13},{"id":181,"text":"Even then , he maintained","depth":12},{"id":182,"text":"that he did not discuss his personal views of the Mueller inquiry .","depth":12},{"id":183,"text":"He was ultimately hired as Sessions ' chief of staff in October 2017 .","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"Whitaker has presided over a period","depth":6},{"id":185,"text":"in which tandem criminal investigations around the president have intensified .","depth":6},{"id":186,"text":"Under his watch , Mueller ' s office arrested Stone , Trump ' s longtime adviser , on charges","depth":7},{"id":187,"text":"of lying to Congress about his efforts","depth":8},{"id":188,"text":"to learn about emails","depth":9},{"id":189,"text":"the Russian government hacked during the 2016 campaign .","depth":9},{"id":190,"text":"A separate team of prosecutors said in a court filing","depth":7},{"id":191,"text":"that Trump ' s former personal lawyer , Michael Cohen , made illegal hush-money payments to two women \" at the direction of \" Trump .","depth":7},{"id":192,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":193,"text":"Incoming House committee chairman threatens to subpoena acting attorney general Matthew Whitaker","depth":5},{"id":194,"text":"More :","depth":4},{"id":195,"text":"What has new Acting Attorney General Matt Whitaker said about the Mueller investigation ?","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":391,"left":0,"right":390,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":390,"left":378,"right":389,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":378,"left":266,"right":377,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":213,"right":265,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":213,"left":207,"right":212,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":202,"right":206,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":198,"right":201,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":1,"right":197,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":197,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":201,"left":4,"right":200,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":5,"right":199,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":206,"left":203,"right":205,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":8,"rig